Stadium Ticket RESTful API for POSIX Operating Systems

0.  To install dependencies:

    scripts/install-dependencies.sh

1.  To initialize the database schema:

    scripts/sql.sh [schema-mysql|schema-sqlite]

2.  To reset the database to a known state:

    scripts/sql.sh [reset-mysql|reset-sqlite]

3.  To run the unit tests:

    scripts/run.sh python3 -m unittest discover

4.  To start the app:

    scripts/run.sh flask run

5.  To test the app:

    scripts/app-test.sh

6.  To stress test the app:

    scripts/load-test.sh

7.  To build and run a Docker container:

    scripts/run.sh docker-compose up --build
